{"tid":1006332,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何家傳統年三十晚要唔瞓覺「守歲」　何超蓮：寓意Daddy身體健康","createTime":"2019-02-03T02:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T06:58:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"b2507282a4d16e7326d774f54d611411e6d90298","tid":1006332,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:22:26.000Z","msg":"何超蓮今日（2/2）出席在銅鑼灣的日本著名甜品旗艦店開幕典禮，獲邀擔任剪綵嘉賓，更即場顯身手炮製甜品。超蓮笑言自己超級喜歡食甜品：「今朝7點幾落機返嚟，基本上攰到傻咗，但都要嚟支持一下，因為實在太鍾意食甜品，呢間我係日本有食過，真係好好食。」<br />\n農曆新年前，原來超蓮有個傳統習俗，每逢年三十晚都要「守歲」。超蓮直言：「『守歲』嘅意思，代表唔瞓覺，嗰日我哋基本上係攞正牌唔瞓覺，寓意對Daddy媽咪嘅身體健康會好好，今年就特別啲啦開咗間牛肉麵店，咁所以我唔瞓嘅同時，會留喺舖度打點，如果大家行完年宵肚餓，就過嚟我度搵我食下嘢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2399999/org/1937076c4af00623113cd5c3a12e6d55.JPG/HuXs417Ur7QQQpSXLDkJV7fgTwfEIp_AYYr-Y2GK_mM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2399999%2Forg%2F1937076c4af00623113cd5c3a12e6d55.JPG%2FHuXs417Ur7QQQpSXLDkJV7fgTwfEIp_AYYr-Y2GK_mM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=6b90e238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2399984/org/26ca63fef93dbd1e944ac8956780f681.JPG/tXHlJWHoI3spSyDGOWX0vaf002-1KEeJWpxIeHCcSHg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2399984%2Forg%2F26ca63fef93dbd1e944ac8956780f681.JPG%2FtXHlJWHoI3spSyDGOWX0vaf002-1KEeJWpxIeHCcSHg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0ede41ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c135ddbd232d0c85bb409a8cc25526ce5fae60fd","tid":1006332,"uid":5499,"like":204,"dislike":0,"score":204,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"守夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7474adc333f7d9e104ca6bd3ed0c6b29ff2c76","tid":1006332,"uid":29093,"like":131,"dislike":2,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:35:43.000Z","msg":"分身家了"},{"pid":"ba76de24b4b80c7b72a69af9758714897884c2ef","tid":1006332,"uid":52874,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTim